rComments: His grading is really easy and lectures are super chill. I used the textbook but am still unsure if I needed to. He's a nice guy, and tests are super straight forward.
Best prof I've had, amazing lectures and materials are well-explained. 10/10 loved his class
Ryan Webb is seriously awesome! Reasonable grader, good presenter, engages the class very well and pretty funny. Definitely recommend taking marketing with him!
Nice prof. Nice lecture. Good mark.
Chill prof. Gives good grades but lectures are sort of boring and dated.

Prof. Webb is amazing! Super funny and great lectures. The class is small so you can really engage in group discussions and he does a great job of keeping the lectures interesting (instead of just reading off his slides). Make sure you participate in discussions.

Professor Webb is a solid lecturer. He does not allow cellphones or laptops to be used in class (the only professor who's ever said no to both during my 4 years). He can be strict/rude at times. He is an easy marker by Rotman standards (B+ class average). This course is very easy relative to others so I do recommend taking it with him.

Great prof! Really cool guy. He's clear with his content and interacts with the class all throughout lecture. He ensures we get the material but he's not that easy! His tests are fair and makes the content fun.
